was the shift happening inside him.\n\nHe stopped chasing.\nHe started aligning.\n\nYears later, right on time, he received $10 million for his role in “Dumb and Dumber.”\n\nThat wasn’t luck.\nThat was a trained mind.\n\nI think about this whenever I hear stories of people stuck in survival mode — like a cash-on-delivery rider delivering packages all day, touching money that never stays with him, believing wealth is only for others.\n\nUntil he changes one thing.\n\nHis focus.\n\nA few quiet minutes each morning.\nNo phone.\nNo noise.\n\nJust intention, gratitude, and belief.\n\nNot to force money…\nbut to become the person who attracts it.\n\nBecause money doesn’t respond to struggle.\nIt responds to clarity.\n\nIf you’re working hard but feel stuck, maybe your effort isn’t the problem.\n\nMaybe your mindset is asking for an upgrade.\n\nIf you’re curious about manifestation and abundance consciousness…\n\nExplore it yourself. Click the link in bio\n@lawsofattraction2026\n\n#manifestation\n#moneymindset\n#abundance\n#lawofattraction\n#wealthconsciousnes", "duration": 76.182, "timestamp": 1770955884, "uploader_id": "79661276513", "uploader": "Manifestation||Affirmation", "channel": "lawsofattraction2026", "like_count": 7177, "comment_count": 128, "comments": [{"author": "davidbudhram", "author_id": "2103956897", "id": "18385636288088863", "text": "👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1775085326}, {"author": "the_barefootwarrior", "author_id": "37329636085", "id": "18114291577671212", "text": "🙌", "timestamp": 1774824787}, {"author": "gentle_positive_reminders_", "author_id": "73660828160", "id": "18157928371438637", "text": "🔥❤️🙌❤️🔥", "timestamp": 1774738428}, {"author": "tammy_karisma", "author_id": "2324466885", "id": "18041940452765441", "text": "❤️🙌🔥👏", "timestamp": 1774688051}, {"author": "cgmorrall", "author_id": "53454569", "id": "17929378299084414", "text": "🙌 Love this 😍", "timestamp": 1774227678}, {"author": "sunshinethemommager", "author_id": "497772064", "id": "18111589081